{"tid":2498499,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"觀塘海濱音樂噴泉明日起啟用　每日分時段表演","createTime":"2021-04-21T08:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T08:24:22.000Z","uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8954bde451194e91007c679641601c6a9331540c","tid":2498499,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:11:18.000Z","msg":"佔地約3740平方米的觀塘海濱音樂噴泉，明日起啟用。音樂噴泉以電腦程式控制，逢周一至五有3節表演時段，周六、日及公眾假期有5節表演時段。<br />\n<br />\n立法會財委會於2018年11月批出涉款近<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">5000萬元</span></span></strong>的觀塘海濱音樂噴泉項目。當局表示，噴泉是第四屆觀塘區議會建議推行的<strong><span class=\"red\">社區重點項目計劃</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n噴泉內有3個互動嬉水區，各嬉水區內設有感應裝置，當感應到遊人接近時，不同花式的噴咀會噴出形態各異的水柱，讓遊人互動玩樂。音樂噴泉及互動嬉水區會在每日早上8時半至晚上10時半運作，音樂噴泉逢周一至五更有3節表演時段，周六、日及及公眾假期更會加開2節表演。<br />\n<br />\n現屆觀塘區議會曾要求暫停工程。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘海濱音樂噴泉表演時間表<br />\n周一至五: 13:30,   19:30,   20:30<br />\n周六、日及公眾假期: 10:30, 13:30, 19:30,  20:30,  21:30<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210421/461565344641716224281507.jpeg/Fjr1pv7Q4qdAQ9De7KbBC0YLUQuOrZM8Vb2nYXO9p2E?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210421%2F461565344641716224281507.jpeg%2FFjr1pv7Q4qdAQ9De7KbBC0YLUQuOrZM8Vb2nYXO9p2E%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=90f84822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210421/461565348018262016836974.jpeg/zg2FRgWGJRXjPDm2fjY0biFA2qvuzsOYikeSvqxHkr4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210421%2F461565348018262016836974.jpeg%2Fzg2FRgWGJRXjPDm2fjY0biFA2qvuzsOYikeSvqxHkr4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7f6531bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210421/461565353563394048146795.jpeg/Bg1M0OIjvNYp03bnOG7iOMFdwmQepVzC9sN5PNDDeTw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210421%2F46156535356339404814679